## 📂 Run Folder Structure

Each run folder follows this structure:

```
runs/[RUN-ID]/
├─ README.md                      ← Start here: run overview & key decisions
├─ run_metadata.json              ← Machine-readable run info
├─ run_log.json                   ← Execution log (timeline)
├─ artifacts/                     ← All produced artifacts
│  ├─ user_stories.md
│  ├─ vision_and_scope.md
│  └─ ...
├─ decisions/
│  ├─ approval_decisions.json     ← Who approved what
│  ├─ consultation_requests.json  ← Questions asked
│  └─ consultation_responses.json ← Answers received
└─ results/
   ├─ artifact_state.json         ← Which artifacts were completed
   ├─ informed_role_briefs.json   ← Who was notified
   └─ expert_context.json         ← Expert inputs used
```

